               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Kumarēcacatakam</title>, by <persName xml:lang="ta">Kurupāta Tācar</persName> (Zvelebil 1995, p. 387).</p>
<p>The text is incomplete. The manuscript stops short in U2, f25r, with the beginning of stanza 48, whereas in U2, f25v, unblackened, we find only the intetitle and the the first letters of the stanza.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (February 2021 and June 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
